  <description><![CDATA[<p>Boutique in style the Hotel Santa Margherita Palace has a crisp and modern feel matched with all the comforts you would expect from a 5 star hotel, attention to detail is all part of the Italian hospitality. 100m from the promenade and 5km from Portofino allowing you to explore everything that <a data-udi="umb://document/a2efda6a9a1e4affa8c542627565b55e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a2efda6a9a1e4affa8c542627565b55e}" title="Santa Margherita">Santa Margherita</a> has to offer. Restaurant Francy serves a fantastic menu of Italian culinary delights with an international haute cuisine twist. The lounge bar and garden give ample space for you to stretch back and relax and the exclusive Spa a haven for treatments and relaxation.</p>]]></description>
